Installation / First run:

Windows: 

Just execute the 'scc.exe'
You should do this in FULLSCREEN mode to improve the speed.
In order to do this, press ALT+ENTER.
To cancel the calculation press CTRL+C.

Linux: 

Just type 'make' and then './scc'
You should do this in FULLSCREEN mode to improve the speed.
To cancel the calculation press CTRL+C
scc.exe won't work correctly with the Windowsemulator 'WINE'.


	

